  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="sonnet">
        <lg type="1st quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Like the waves make it to the graveled coast,</l>
            <l>So our minutes run to their end,</l>
            <l>Every changing place with that which comes earlier,</l>
            <l>In <choice><orig>sequents</orig><reg>sequence</reg></choice> hard work brings you <choice><orig>torwards</orig><reg>towards</reg></choice> to the fight.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="2nd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Nativity, once in the focus of light,</l>
            <l>Matures, and being crowned,</l>
            <l>Twisted eclipses against his glory fight,</l>
            <l>And the time spent, his gift now <choice><orig>suprissed</orig><reg>suppressed</reg></choice>.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="3rd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>And time paralyses the look of youth,</l>
            <l>And searches the parallels in his beauty,</l>
            <l>Feeds onthe specialities of nature's truth,</l>
            <l>And there is nothing left <choice><orig>exept</orig><reg>except</reg></choice> the grass to cut.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="final couplet">
          <s>
            <l>And I hope my verse will last forever,</l>
            <l>Praising your worth, in spite of his cruel hand.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
